column4: Short fairy tale: Once upon a time, a guy asked a beautiful girl, 'Will you marry me" The girl said, 'NO!' And the guy lived happily ever after and rode motorcycles and went fishing and hunting and played golf a lot and drank beer and scotch and had tons of money in the bank and left the toilet seat up and farted whenever he wanted.
granted but this channel is for ubuntu support, not stupid lame jokes :)
